Name: go_memstats_heap_idle_bytes

Description: Number of bytes in use by mcache structures.

Description: Number of bytes allocated and still in use.

Name: go_memstats_mspan_inuse_bytes
Description: Number of bytes in use by mspan structures.

Description: Number of bytes used for garbage collection system metadata.

Description: Number of heap bytes allocated and still in use.

Name: go_memstats_heap_sys_bytes
Description: Number of heap bytes obtained from system.

Description: Number of bytes obtained from system.

Name: go_memstats_heap_inuse_bytes

Description: Number of heap bytes released to OS.

Description: Number of bytes used for mspan structures obtained from system.

Name: coredns_health_request_failures_total
Description: The number of times the health check failed.

Name: coredns_local_localhost_requests_total
Description: Counter of localhost.<domain> requests.

Name: coredns_panics_total
Description: A metrics that counts the number of panics.

Name: coredns_health_request_duration_seconds
Description: Histogram of the time (in seconds) each request took.

Name: coredns_build_info
Description: A metric with a constant '1' value labeled by version, revision, and goversion from which CoreDNS was built.

Name: coredns_reload_failed_total
Description: Counter of the number of failed reload attempts.

Name: coredns_plugin_enabled
Description: A metric that indicates whether a plugin is enabled on per server and zone basis.

Name: coredns_forward_max_concurrent_rejects_total
Description: Counter of the number of queries rejected because the concurrent queries were at maximum.

Name: coredns_hosts_reload_timestamp_seconds
Description: The timestamp of the last reload of hosts file.

Name: coredns_forward_healthcheck_broken_total
Description: Counter of the number of complete failures of the healthchecks.

Name: process_open_fds

Description: Maximum number of open file descriptors.

Name: process_start_time_seconds
Description: Start time of the process since unix epoch in seconds.

Name: process_cpu_seconds_total
Description: Total user and system CPU time spent in seconds.

Name: process_virtual_memory_bytes
Description: Virtual memory size in bytes.

Name: process_virtual_memory_max_bytes
Description: Maximum amount of virtual memory available in bytes.

Name: scrape_duration_seconds
Description: Duration of the scrape

Name: scrape_samples_post_metric_relabeling
Description: The number of samples remaining after metric relabeling was applied

Name: scrape_series_added
Description: The approximate number of new series in this scrape

Name: go_goroutines
Description: Number of goroutines that currently exist.

Name: up
Description: The scraping was successful

Name: go_threads
Description: Number of OS threads created.

Name: go_info
Description: Information about the Go environment.

Name: go_gc_duration_seconds
